if Fraser's Ridge is near...

56:16.580 --> 56:18.536
Someone's coming. Someone's coming!

56:21.120 --> 56:22.280
It's Tom Burley.

56:36.850 --> 56:37.839
Get rid of him.

56:37.970 --> 56:38.971
Should I kill him?

56:39.060 --> 56:41.767
No. No, I won't make a murderer of you.

56:43.230 --> 56:44.891
Not that he doesn't deserve it.

56:50.570 --> 56:52.401
One, two, three.

56:58.040 --> 56:59.029
Go.

56:59.700 --> 57:01.076
What d'ye want me to do wi' him?

57:01.160 --> 57:02.161
I dinna care.

57:02.250 --> 57:03.740
Just get him out of my sight.
